\n唔係掛我聽日一次過睇多次係邊款ram<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁假設真係兩條都ddr4又有咁嘅情況又係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17183629a4d3ea18f208a031746bf75dae78c37","tid":482940,"uid":9021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:22:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬用呢塊？<br />\nASRock B150M Combo-G<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過需要注意的是，雖然實現了混合兼容，但不能混插，因為內存模塊不同並不能夠同時工作，這幾乎是必然的事情，因為每一代內存都採用了不同的引腳，不同的延遲根本無法協同工作，而且電壓也不同（ DDR3 的標準電壓是1.5V，DDR3L、DDR4 則都是 1.35V）。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/MyJay.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FMyJay.html&d=DstuGdSe1pRyRRMD08SOs8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d0e2bcb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/MyJay.html</a>"},{"pid":"e4ed5f535f3baa0f62b2834abd17d53c61c97bc1","tid":482940,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83565ce926da4402e9432b4da45cb7a0b74c8ed0","tid":482940,"uid":81308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬懶醒學人加ram 唔識睇ddr就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry囉電腦野唔太熟啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔熟唔問就買係要交下學費架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4ad57b733194a57f4a7750c3fed93a3f1d30c5","tid":482940,"uid":47877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 數據仔想做隻雞"}]}